{{Box|text=
Add {{project_name_long}} Repository.

Choose either: Option <u>A</u>, Option <u>B</u> <u>'''OR'''</u> Option <u>C</u>.
{{Box|text=
<div class="toccolours mw-collapsible mw-collapsed">
'''Option <u>A</u>''': Add {{project_name_long}} Onion Repository.

To add {{project_name_long}} Repository over Onion please press on expand on the right.

<div class="mw-collapsible-content">
Install apt-transport-tor from the Debian repository.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo apt install apt-transport-tor
}}

Add [[Project-APT-Repository|{{project_name_long}} APT repository]] for default {{project_name_long}} using Debian {{Code2|stable}}. At the time of writing this was <code>{{Stable_project_version_based_on_Debian_codename}}</code>.

{{CodeSelect|code=
echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/derivative.asc] tor+http://deb.{{project_onion}} {{Stable_project_version_based_on_Debian_codename}} main contrib non-free" {{!}} sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/derivative.list
}}
</div>
</div>
}}

{{Box|text=
<div class="toccolours mw-collapsible mw-collapsed">
'''Option <u>B</u>''': Add {{project_name_long}} Clearnet Repository over Tor.

To add {{project_name_long}} Repository over torified clearnet please press on expand on the right.
<div class="mw-collapsible-content">
Install <code>apt-transport-tor</code> from the Debian repository.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo apt install apt-transport-tor
}}

Add {{project_name_long}} APT repository for default {{project_name_long}} using Debian stable. At the time of writing this was <code>{{Stable_project_version_based_on_Debian_codename}}</code>.

{{CodeSelect|code=
echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/derivative.asc] tor+https://deb.{{project_clearnet}} {{Stable_project_version_based_on_Debian_codename}} main contrib non-free" {{!}} sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/derivative.list
}}
</div>
</div>
}}

{{Box|text=
<div class="toccolours mw-collapsible mw-collapsed">
'''Option <u>C</u>''': Add {{project_name_short}} Clearnet Repository over clearnet.

To add {{project_name_long}} Repository over clearnet please press on expand on the right.
<div class="mw-collapsible-content">
Add {{project_name_long}} APT repository for default {{project_name_long}} using Debian stable. At the time of writing this was <code>{{Stable_project_version_based_on_Debian_codename}}</code>.

{{CodeSelect|code=
echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/derivative.asc] https://deb.{{project_clearnet}} {{Stable_project_version_based_on_Debian_codename}} main contrib non-free" {{!}} sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/derivative.list
}}
</div>
</div>
}}
}}